The paper presents a novel approach for predicting anticancer compound sensitivity using multi-modal attention-based neural networks. The approach involves integrating molecular structure, transcriptomic profiles, and prior knowledge about interactions among proteins within cells. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational biology (cs.CE), databases (cs.DB), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
